We had a small amplifi white cube and two extenders. The internet speed was horrible, constant overlap and distruptions, random crashes, without a reboot very very low internet speeds, constantly on the 2.4GHz instead of the 5. Maybe if you throw more money at it, the experience improves, but I do not recommend people buy this brand.
We switched to a Unifi router and wifi access points and it works like a charm. The access points can be plugged in ethernet wall sockets and give a 4 ethernetport uitput too!
